    /// <summary>
    /// Claw device: a socket server (HTTP) that listens on a configurable port.
    /// Protocol: receives JSON, returns JSON.
    /// Supports POST /authenticate {user,password} => {token} with progressive lockout.
    /// Supports POST /entrypoint (bearer auth) {method, data:{command,...}} dispatching to registered AGI procedures.
